momentum-mouse (0.5.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New setting for virtual trackpad resolution
  * New setting for refresh rate
  * GUI now runs as root to avoid asking for password each settings change
  * GUI for selecting a mouse device
  * GUI Sliders for resolution and refresh rate settings
  * GUI Visual feedback on successful applied settings

 -- Ash Martian <dev@ashmartian.com> Sat, 15 Mar 2025 15:00 +0000

